 />\n諗好多深層野 又會好多野諗多左<br />\n識左佢之後反而少左胡思亂想"},{"pid":"f1b211432cac47ca2dce73de7b105868bb46fa7a","tid":707492,"uid":21948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"點樣先可以搵到soulmate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1dd9bd5b72962e4a698a41279c18a128142118","tid":707492,"uid":79836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1b211432cac47ca2dce73de7b105868bb46fa7a","tid":707492,"uid":21948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"點樣先可以搵到soulmate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"Soulmate 應該只能遇上不能找到"}]}